\int_{a}^b \vert \alpha x + \beta \vert^2 \, dx \leq (b-a) \left( \vert \alpha a + \beta \vert^2 + \vert \alpha b + \beta \vert^2 \right)
\alpha,\beta\in\mathbb{R}
f(x)=(\alpha x+\beta)^2
[a,b]
a
b
(\alpha x+\beta)^2\leq \max\big\{(\alpha a+\beta)^2,\: (\alpha b+\beta)^2\big\}\leq (\alpha a+\beta)^2+(\alpha b+\beta)^2
\int_a^b (\alpha x+\beta)^2\leq(b-a)\Big((\alpha a+\beta)^2+(\alpha b+\beta)^2\Big)
